    <h3>Earlier</h3>
    <ul class="publications">
      <li><strong>Saeri, A. K.</strong> et al. (2022). <em>What Works to Increase Charitable Donations? A Meta-Review with Meta-Meta-Analysis.</em> VOLUNTAS. <a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s11266-022-00499-y">doi.org/10.1007/s11266-022-00499-y</a></li>
    </ul>

    <p>Full list: <a href="https://scholar.google.com.au/citations?user=B_bJG3kAAAAJ">Google Scholar</a>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="contact">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Please contact me to discuss potential collaborations, briefings, or engagements.</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:alexander@aksaeri.com">alexander@aksaeri.com</a></p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="https://calendar.app.google/sv3Sb5sjUxxTdssv8" class="btn">Request a meeting</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
